Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.20,0:00:15.87,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Pocket Monsters... \N Pokémon for short.{001}{This is Lucius's actor, but the narration isn't written like Lucius}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.71,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,This planet’s strange, strange creatures.{001}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.50,0:00:23.42,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The sky, the sea, forests, cities... {same four environments as 001 but different order}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.42,0:00:27.84,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,You can spot them \N just about anywhere you look.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.18,0:00:32.22,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Some{ of them} live together with humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.22,0:00:35.72,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Others live out in the wild, \N either alone...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.31,0:00:39.44,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,...or in packs with their friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.44,0:00:43.23,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And there are even some \N that live aboard the Brave Asagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.07,0:00:47.90,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,By the way, \N do you know who these Pokémon are?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.57,0:00:53.03,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Yep, it’s Loudbone and Lugarugan. \N Right now, these two...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.24,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,...are incredibly hungry!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.00,0:01:01.54,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hmm? Are they here for \N some secret midnight snack time?
Comment: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:17.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.65,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,You can find tons of stuff you’re not using \N if you just poke around a bit, eh? {ALT: There’s always tons of stuff you’re not using if you just poke around a bit, huh?}{If one searches for them, there's quite a number of things one's not using, aren't there?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.65,0:04:14.73,Main,Orio,0,0,0,,Clean-out events like this are great. \N They make for a nice refresh. {片づける}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.35,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? You’re throwing that out?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.14,0:04:50.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\q2}Didn’t you film with that? \N In a way, that makes it a highly prized collectible, no? {lit: In some sense, that makes it treasured merchandise, right? - aka it'd be a holy grail/collectors item to fans('like me')}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.44,0:04:53.61,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Ehh... I’ve still got \N another ten or so anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.40,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.03,0:05:04.62,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Look, look! I found a super cool rock!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.79,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I’m puttin’ this in my room!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.21,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.67,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.25,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Why not...?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.46,0:05:20.80,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Ooh, you likin’ it too, Yamirami? \N All right! This’s goin’ in my room!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.64,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Like I said, there’s no way. {I told you, you can’t.}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.64,0:05:25.97,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,We’re trying to {\i1}clean out{\i} \N unneeded stuff, you know...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.22,Main,Molly,0,0,0,,Put it back where you found it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.39,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Aww!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.82,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,The ship’s been feeling \N pretty cramped lately as it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.90,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,We can’t go bringing {\i1}more{\i0} aboard...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.19,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.41,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Doesn’t something seem odd here?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.79,0:05:50.79,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.29,0:05:56.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,{\q2}I’ve got more stuff I want to throw away in my room, \N so let’s go grab it{ together}.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.77,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? Did I just...?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.36,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Must’ve imagined it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.86,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Masquernya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.37,0:06:33.50,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Were you trying to hide Metamon?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.25,0:06:34.79,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.75,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,This one I’m keeping...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.92,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And this one I’m not...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.59,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Oh, this is important.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.84,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya, take this for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.43,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Masquernya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.69,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,H-Huh?! Your tail?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.82,0:07:47.99,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Your tail?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.91,0:07:51.45,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Your tail’s {\i1}really{\i0} stretched out!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.62,0:07:54.62,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What?! What? What? What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.38,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I just heard a weird noise!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.05,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What?! What? What? What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.35,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What was all {\i1}that...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.27,0:08:21.61,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Thank goodness... \N I thought you tore it off.{Leave a cat to toss out her own toys... and Liko's diaries}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.33,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.87,0:09:15.45,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Here’s more for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.97,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What’re they racing around for?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.89,0:09:42.85,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.73,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Are there... more than usual?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.88,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,They look like they’re having fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.61,0:10:34.91,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Looks like they decided to ask \N the other Pokémon for help, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.88,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Ahh, I’m starvin’!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.93,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,I wonder what’s for lunch today...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.64,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,I {\i1}have{\i0} been smellin’ something \N for a while now.{uncaptioned}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.64,0:10:59.10,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Ult, what do you think it’ll be?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.31,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.31,0:11:02.31,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Ain’t it gonna be that? \N Y’know, {\i1}that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.41,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Here you go. \N Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.41,0:11:24.58,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.13,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Hey, where’s Lugarugan’s lunch?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.13,0:11:33.21,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Ah... I’ve been letting it taste test \N too much again lately.{Dread Iwanko}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.92,0:11:37.22,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Its belly and jaw \N are getting a bit pudgy...{Dread Iwanko}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.18,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,So Lugarugan’s getting...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.89,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,...the special diet menu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.66,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,I know you don’t like Matoma Berries...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.66,0:11:52.07,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,But they’re healthy, and they’ll make you sweat \N and speed up your metabolism.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.07,0:11:54.23,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,That makes ‘em perfect for dieting.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.82,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Can’t you try them? \N Even just one bite?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.84,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Ooh, you ate them!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.84,0:12:15.67,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,I’m so proud of you. \N Now, all this pudginess will just...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.67,0:12:16.34,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.34,0:12:19.22,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,That feels more {\i1}drippy{\i0} than pudgy...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.73,0:12:29.94,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.98,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.49,0:12:37.99,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.08,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What’s gotten into all of you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.08,0:12:48.91,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,C’mon! Cloth, cloth!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.04,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Huh? Aren’t the Sharitatsu \N being squashed?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.08,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Are they okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.08,0:12:53.38,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Cloth, cloth!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.38,0:12:55.50,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Dekanuchan, calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.50,0:12:59.26,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Hold up, ain’t Yorunozuku’s \N eyebrows fat-lookin’?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.05,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,There you are! Masquernya...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.10,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Have you seen \N my Ikirinko wood carving?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.22,0:13:09.77,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It was about this big, \N or if you include the tail, about {\i1}this{\i0} big...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.81,0:13:16.53,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,And it had this lumpy bit on its head...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,No, I guess you wouldn’t \N know anything about it...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.45,0:13:28.70,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’s so strange, though... \N I was {\i1}sure{\i0} I put it in the box of things to keep...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.50,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I’ll go look one more time!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.09,0:13:43.72,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Well now... \N I wonder how this is all going to turn out...
Comment: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:49.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.02,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,It’s not here...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.23,0:14:43.40,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Oh! You found it for me?! \N Thank you, Masquernya!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.87,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Oh, you know what? \N I found this earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.37,0:14:54.96,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,You used to play with this so much! \N It really takes me back!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.72,0:15:06.34,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,I didn’t know you still liked it, \N Masquernya...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.72,0:15:12.27,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Don’t you worry. \N I’ll make sure to keep it for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.52,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.27,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Time to make one final push!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.24,0:15:31.49,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hmm? Those are some serious faces. \N I wonder what’s about to happen...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.67,0:15:43.76,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Oh, my! It’s purposefully trying \N to get Alolan Betobeton to eat it...{Dread Yukiwarashi}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.76,0:15:46.51,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,...in order to fetch \N the Ikirinko wood carving in its belly!{Dread Betobeton}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.80,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Masquernya?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.42,0:17:09.09,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Hold on! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.93,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.69,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,What’s wrong with Masquernya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.56,0:17:22.65,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.23,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.99,0:17:33.24,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Metamon?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.16,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,A cattail?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.57,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.53,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Whoa, it really is a Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.87,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Gotta wonder \N when it got aboard the ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.75,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,Metamon. Transform Pokémon. \N Normal type.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.13,0:18:30.26,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,It can freely recombine \N its own cellular structure to Transform.{Partial Violet dex entry}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.26,0:18:33.97,Main,Smartphone Rotom,0,0,0,,If it laughs and relaxes, \N its transformation comes undone.{Partial Scarlet dex entry, with 'made to' removed}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.05,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Cool! Ain’t never seen \N a Metamon before!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.80,0:18:38.60,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.28,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.78,0:18:56.82,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.37,0:18:59.79,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Our ship...{lit: This place, [the Brave Asagi]}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.29,0:19:03.75,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,The Brave Asagi... \N You’ve taken a liking to it, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.25,0:19:10.09,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Which is why you all want to \N stay together with Metamon...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.09,0:19:11.76,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Isn’t that right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.91,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Cap gave his okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.71,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard the Brave Asagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.51,Main,Ult,0,0,0,,Let’s get along good, ‘kay...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.51,0:19:55.55,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,...Metamon?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.18,0:20:07.35,Main,Dot,0,0,0,,Is that a souvenir for Ms. Diana{Honorifics note: Diana-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.52,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.52,0:20:11.27,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Grandma likes Ikirinko.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.94,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah... \N It’s good you found that, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.94,0:20:14.44,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.95,Main,Murdock,0,0,0,,Here you go. \N A heaping helping of Matoma Berries!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.40,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,By the way, about Metamon...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.54,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,They turn into a rock \N when they sleep,{General species trait introduced in Sleep}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.54,0:21:13.08,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,so Yamirami and Masquernya \N fight over who gets it at night.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.48,0:21:34.06,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Overcoming countless trials,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.73,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and embracing the delight \N of new encounters,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.28,0:21:39.99,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,the travels of those \N aboard the Brave Asagi...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.99,0:21:42.61,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,...continue on, \N even today.
Comment: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie A}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.33,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Friede here!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.33,0:21:51.87,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s time to Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.92,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Today’s topic is Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.38,0:21:57.42,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,It’s a Pokémon with \N a knack for Transforming,{move name}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.42,0:22:01.51,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,but if two Metamon meet, \N do you know what they do?{but do you know what happens if two Metamon meet? / They run away / They make friends / They fight}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.09,0:22:06.47,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,See the answer after the commercials!
Comment: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:06.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:36.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mega-Study With Instructor Starmie B}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.36,0:23:42.28,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,Time to announce \N the correct answer!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.28,0:23:43.86,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.86,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,C: {They }Fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.86,0:23:51.62,Main,Friede,0,0,0,,{\q2}They can Transform and make friends with anyone, \N but apparently Metamon don’t get along with other Metamon!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.62,0:23:52.74,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.58,0:23:59.33,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,When they meet up, \N they get into Transform contests!
Comment: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.59,0:24:03.88,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Yo-ssu! All you Pokémon Trainers out there!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.88,0:24:05.38,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Eek! Gurumin!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.38,0:24:10.68,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,{\q2}Since Metamon’s our new pal, how ‘bout comin’ in for a min \N to have some Gurumin bread together?{minmin}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.68,0:24:13.68,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Gurumin bread? \N Gurumin’s gonna become bread?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.68,0:24:16.43,Main,Gurumin,0,0,0,,Let’s go see all sorts of Pokémon bread \N at the Bread Fest!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.43,0:24:18.65,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Wahh!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.02,0:24:22.15,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,And so, to be continued \N next time on Pocket Monsters!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.15,0:24:24.32,Main,Roy,0,0,0,,Bread, Bread, Bread! Mini Gurumin!!{panpanpanpan pokemon pan seems to be a Pokemon pan phrase, and panpanpanpan anpanman an anpanman phrase.}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.32,0:24:26.15,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh? Mini Gurumin?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.15,0:24:28.41,Main,Liko,0,0,0,,Huh?! What is that?!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
